closer.dateline:
Subscribed and sworn to before me, a notary
                            public in and for the District of Columbia, this 13th day of April,
                                1892.

frus:attachment.p:
Henry Treadwell, being duly sworn, says that he is a citizen of the United;
                        States, is 70 years of age, and resides in the city of Brooklyn, in the
                        State of New York.
